OL,5, Diane Abbott has said comments         
OL,6, allegedly made by a top Tory donor that
OL,7, the MP made him "want to hate all black
OL,8, women" and that she needed "to be shot"
OL,9, were "frightening".                    
OL,11,FBritain's longest-serving black MP said
OL,12,Fthe "fact that two MPs have been       
OL,13,Fmurdered in recent years makes talk    
OL,14,Flike this all the more alarming".      
OL,16,FAccording to the Guardian, Frank Hester
OL,17,Fmade the comments at a meeting in 2019.
OL,19,FMr Hester has apologised for making    
OL,20,F"rude" comments about Ms Abbott.       
